sks. Every little noise or movement can easily distract him and it is a challenge for him to return to the task at hand.\",\"image_space\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":10},\"hover_animation\":\"shrink\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"19\",\"right\":\"19\",\"bottom\":\"19\",\"left\":\"3\",\"isLinked\":false},\"_background_background\":\"classic\",\"_background_color\":\"#ffffff\",\"_border_border\":\"solid\",\"_border_radius\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"1\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"1\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_border_hover_border\":\"solid\",\"_border_hover_color\":\"#28aae1\",\"_border_radius_hover\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"1\",\"right\":\"1\",\"bottom\":\"1\",\"left\":\"1\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_box_shadow_hover_box_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"_box_shadow_hover_box_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":0,\"vertical\":0,\"blur\":14,\"spread\":0,\"color\":\"\"},\"position\":\"left\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"},{\"id\":\"a21704f\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">What is common in all these cases is the fact that these kids are dealing with difficulties maintaining their focus, behavior and attention, and might have ADHD (Attention Deficit Hyperactivity Disorder).<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"77aeec6\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"30\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"30\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"01bc2ef\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4d850c3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><strong>The system will automatically produce three reports for each\\u00a0student, these reports are associated with the\\u00a0student\'s Individual attention profile.<\\/strong><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"8843d2d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/icon_3.png\",\"id\":199},\"title_text\":\"Teacher report\",\"description_text\":\"With comparative results and suggested techniques that the teacher can implement in class for the specific student and that can assist his learning.\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Axon-School_Techers-report_example.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Click for an example &gt;&gt;<\\/a>\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Axon-School_Techers-report_example.pdf\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\"},\"position\":\"left\",\"image_size\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":16}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"},{\"id\":\"35908b6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/icon_4.png\",\"id\":200},\"title_text\":\"Parent report\",\"description_text\":\"suggesting techniques parents can use at home to strengthen their student social and learning abilities.<br><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/409_parents_report-2.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Click for an example &gt;&gt;<\\/a>\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/409_parents_report-2.pdf\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\"},\"position\":\"left\",\"image_size\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":16}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"},{\"id\":\"f0dfb4b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/icon_5.png\",\"id\":201},\"title_text\":\"student report\",\"description_text\":\"The third report goes to the student himself. This time, showing the student this strengths and weaknesses in regards to his attention, suggesting technics that could make a difference in his life. <br><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Axon-School_ParentStudent-report_example.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Click for an example &gt;&gt;<\\/a>\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Axon-School_ParentStudent-report_example.pdf\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\"},\"position\":\"left\",\"image_size\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":16}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"},{\"id\":\"16e7323\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>School Counselors have additional benefits from the system allowing them an aggregated view of the entire class and grade. For more information go to <a href=\\\"#School strategies.\\\"><em><u>School strategies<\\/u><\\/em>.<\\/a><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"50ffc73\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#f2f2f2\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":true},\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"30\",\"right\":\"30\",\"bottom\":\"30\",\"left\":\"30\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b4aba24\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100,\"_inline_size\":null,\"_inline_size_tablet\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fdbcdb1\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/girl-in-classroom.jpg\",\"id\":116}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"7bd5751\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"anchor\":\"School strategies.\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"menu-anchor\"},{\"id\":\"5340873\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>School Strategies<\\/h3><p>AXON-School\\u2122 integrates a comprehensive view of the entire classroom and of the entire grade. These can be especially useful for class behavioral and performance management by the teacher and for the same management on a grade level usually done by a school counselor. <br \\/>Try to recall a class you have been teaching that were notorious around school for being very difficult and noisy, this could be a very frustrating class, and many teachers feel that they do not possess the right tools to deal with such a class. We know that the attentional profile of a class could be an important starting point for a change. Imagine that based on the test results you find out that around 40% of your students are Impulsive-Hyperactive, and that many of them are highly distracted by visual stimulation. This knowledge can dramatically change the way you perceive your class, and we even make suggestions on what could work better in such a case.<\\/p><p><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Axon-School-counselor-report.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\"> Click here for an example of such a report.<\\/a><\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
