_5.png\",\"id\":201},\"title_text\":\"A child report\",\"description_text\":\"The third report goes to the child himself. This time, showing the child his strengths and weaknesses in regards to his attention, suggesting technics that could make a difference in his life. <br><b>Click for an example &gt;&gt;<\\/b>\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"https:\\/\\/axon.digitalim.co.il\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2017\\/12\\/Axon-School_ParentStudent-report_example.pdf\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\"},\"position\":\"left\",\"image_size\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":16}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image-box\"},{\"id\":\"16e7323\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>School Counselors have additional benefits from the system allowing them an aggregated view of the entire class and grade. For more information go to <em><u>School strategies<\\/u><\\/em>.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"50ffc73\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\",\"background_background\":\"classic\",\"background_color\":\"#f2f2f2\",\"margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":0,\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":0,\"isLinked\":true},\"padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"30\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"30\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b4aba24\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"5340873\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<h3>School Strategies<\\/h3><p>AXON-School\\u2122 integrates a comprehensive view of the entire classroom and of the entire grade. These can be especially useful for class behavioral and performance management by the teacher and for the same management on a grade level usually done by a school counselor. <br \\/>Try to recall a class you have been teaching that were notorious around school for being very difficult and noisy, this could be a very frustrating class, and m