(340, 1, '2017-12-28 09:14:10', '2017-12-28 09:14:10', 'This is an example page. It\'s different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:\n\n<blockquote>Hi there! I\'m a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin\' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>\n\n...or something like this:\n\n<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>\n\nAs a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-admin/\">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!', 'Sample Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-28 09:14:10', '2017-12-28 09:14:10', '', 2, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/2017/12/28/2-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(427, 1, '2017-12-28 11:47:49', '2017-12-28 11:47:49', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Attention Test that is at the heart of the system is brought to you by Neurotech Solutions, a world leader in the field of attention, and as such, substantial clinical and developmental efforts have been invested in the test in order to maximize its accuracy and usefulness.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our attention test is a standardized, comparative, Continuous Performance Test. The test is on-line, and requires only an internet connected PC and a set of headphones.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>You can run two versions:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The system will choose the test </strong><strong>automatically</strong><strong> based on the child’s date </strong><strong>Of birth</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img title=\"icon_1\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/icon_1.png\" alt=\"icon_1\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>ONE FOR CHILDREN (6-12)</h3>\r\n14 minutes\r\n<figure><img title=\"icon_2\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/icon_2.png\" alt=\"icon_2\" /></figure>\r\n<h3>ONE FOR TEENS (13-18)</h3>\r\n18 minutes\r\n<h6>The child needs to react by pressing the spacebar to a target element. In the children version</h6>\r\nthey should react to a target of a figure we call HYPER\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/target-children.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"213\" height=\"194\" />\r\n\r\nor to a card of 3 hearts for the teens version\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/target-adults.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"275\" />\r\n\r\nny other element that appears at the center should be ignored\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/non-target-giraff.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 314px) 100vw, 314px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/non-target-giraff.jpg 314w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/non-target-giraff-230x300.jpg 230w\" alt=\"\" width=\"314\" height=\"409\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/non-target-card.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"208\" height=\"275\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/target-children.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"213\" height=\"194\" />\r\n\r\nOh, and these distractors\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/distractor-baby.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"206\" height=\"218\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/distractor-car.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 372px) 100vw, 372px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/distractor-car.jpg 372w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/distractor-car-300x200.jpg 300w\" alt=\"\" width=\"372\" height=\"248\" />\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/plane-distractor.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"273\" height=\"193\" />\r\n\r\n…will do whatever they can to distract the child from focusing on his task.', 'The AXON-School™ test of Attention', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '162-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-28 11:47:49', '2017-12-28 11:47:49', '', 162, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/2017/12/28/162-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(319, 1, '2017-12-28 08:47:24', '2017-12-28 08:47:24', '\n			<ul>\n				<li title=\"Edit Widget\">\n				</li>\n									<li title=\"Duplicate Widget\">\n						Duplicate Widget\n					</li>\n									<li title=\"Save Widget\">\n						Save Widget\n					</li>\n									<li title=\"Remove Widget\">\n						Remove Widget\n					</li>\n							</ul>\n		<h3>Using the system in a school setting</h3><p>The AXON-School™ system is designed to be used for the entire school once a year. Were the system has been used so far we learn that the cycle of a batch of children performing the test is usually 30 minutes which includes a short intro made by the teacher, logging-in, running through the on-screen instructions, performing a short practice session and finally performing the test.</p><p>This process is very easy to manage, as the system runs automatically through most of the session. As a teacher you will not require any unusual technical skills to operate the system.</p><p>We recommend a maximum number of 20 children per batch, provided that each child has enough space to perform the test without overlooking the monitor of a neighboring child.</p><p>Each child will require a dedicated internet connected PC, a monitor and a headset.</p><p>Results are funneled into the system immediately and automatically.</p>', 'USING THE SYSTEM IN A SCHOOL SETTING', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'using-the-system-in-a-school-setting', '', '', '2017-12-28 08:47:24', '2017-12-28 08:47:24', '', 0, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/?elementor_library=using-the-system-in-a-school-setting', 0, 'elementor_library', '', 0),
