(162, 1, '2017-12-26 10:26:17', '2017-12-26 10:26:17', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Attention Test that is at the heart of the system is brought to you by Neurotech Solutions, a world leader in the field of attention, and as such, substantial clinical and developmental efforts have been invested in the test in order to maximize its accuracy and usefulness.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our attention test is a standardized, comparative, Continuous Performance Test. The test is on-line, and requires only an internet connected PC and a set of headphones. </p>		\n			<h2>You can run two versions:</h2>		\n		<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The system will choose the test </strong><strong>automatically</strong><strong> based on the child’s date </strong><strong>Of birth</strong></p>		\n			<figure><img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/icon_1.png\" alt=\"icon_1\" title=\"icon_1\"></figure><h3>ONE FOR CHILDREN (6-12)</h3><p>14 minutes</p>		\n			<figure><img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/icon_2.png\" alt=\"icon_2\" title=\"icon_2\"></figure><h3>ONE FOR TEENS  (13-18)</h3><p>18 minutes</p>		\n		<img width=\"775\" height=\"286\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Untitled-1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Untitled-1.png 775w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Untitled-1-300x111.png 300w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/Untitled-1-768x283.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" />		\n		', 'The AXON-School™ test of Attention', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-axon-school-test-of-attention', '', '', '2018-01-01 08:46:40', '2018-01-01 08:46:40', '', 33, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/?page_id=162', 0, 'page', '', 0),
