(329, 1, '2017-12-28 08:53:42', '2017-12-28 08:53:42', '\n					<h1>\n					</h1>\n							\"The AXON-School is a good exercise to know your class and the children in it. Using this tool we can work as a school to improve the students\' performance.\nIn order to better understand the child, the teacher should be fully equipped with the reports as attention span is very important in today\'s life for getting better results\"\n							<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tt_1.png\" alt=\"tt_1\" />\n													Educational team member\n													The Millennium School, Gurgaon, India.\n		<img width=\"165\" height=\"46\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tt_2.png\" alt=\"\" />		\n							\"It is important to know about our own attention – it helps us in certain ways. I want to find ways to improve my attention\"\n							<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tt_3.png\" alt=\"tt_3\" />\n													Hylav pratavsi Student\n													The Millennium School, Gurgaon, India.\n		<img width=\"165\" height=\"46\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tt_2.png\" alt=\"\" />		\n							\"We see AXON-School as a professional educational tool. Axon-School helps the educational team overachieve educational targets in a professional and measurable way, giving us the ability to advance every student and maximize his or hers abilities\"\n							<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tt_4.png\" alt=\"tt_4\" />\n													Mrs. Levana Milon School principle\n													Mofet Ramot Alon, Jerusalem, Israel.\n		<img width=\"133\" height=\"100\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/tt_5.jpg\" alt=\"\" />		\n		', 'TESTIMONIALS', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'testimonials', '', '', '2017-12-28 08:54:59', '2017-12-28 08:54:59', '', 33, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/?page_id=329', 0, 'page', '', 0),
