(283, 1, '2017-12-28 07:10:59', '2017-12-28 07:10:59', '<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_2.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_2.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_2-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nI’m mostly distracted by my own thoughts.\r\nI can work on something important and suddenly have this great idea that has nothing to do with my task which makes me drop everything and refocus on the idea…\r\n\r\n<strong>Ohad Lavi, CEO</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_54.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_54.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_54-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nI can be very focused and engaged in a conversation, until something triggers a thought about a task I need to take care of… I usually make sure not to forget it and only then can refocus on the conversation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Maggi Rubin Cohen, VP Product Management  </strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_7.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_7.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_7-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nAlthough Emails and phone calls are a major distractor and part of my work; staying connected with our customers is a key and I usually stop everything and give them my professional answer and solution\r\n\r\n<strong>Eran Sandel, VP Sales</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_1.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_1.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_1-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nUbuntu... Ubuntu… Ubuntu…\r\n\r\n<strong>Philip Belder, CTO</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_8.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_8.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_8-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nStaying focused in my work is very important.\r\nHowever, if I hear a song in the background that does not fit the atmosphere, I need to change it to ensure our customers and company receive the best support I can provide…\r\n\r\n<strong>Aviram Salomon, QA Manager</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_3.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_3.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_3-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nI’m mostly distracted by trying to juggle five things at a time.\r\nTrying to accomplish too many tasks can certainly make me lose focus…\r\n\r\n<strong>Noga Mann, Customer Relations Representative</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_4.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_4.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_4-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nDisorganization can make me lose focus. When things are not organized the way I am used too I get easily distracted.\r\n\r\n<strong>Megi Franko, office and HR Manager</strong>\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_6.png\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_6.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_6-150x150.png 150w\" alt=\"\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\r\n\r\nI often find myself being distracted by my cell phone even when it\'s completely silent…  Overtime, I have learned to hide it from sight, especially while working on attention- consuming projects.\r\n\r\n<strong>Keren Peleg, Product Manager</strong>', 'Our team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '272-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-28 07:10:59', '2017-12-28 07:10:59', '', 272, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/2017/12/28/272-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(282, 1, '2017-12-28 07:09:56', '2017-12-28 07:09:56', '\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_2.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_2.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_2-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>I’m mostly distracted by my own thoughts.<br />I can work on something important and suddenly have this great idea that has nothing to do with my task which makes me drop everything and refocus on the idea…</p><p><strong>Ohad Lavi, CEO</strong></p>		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_54.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_54.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_54-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>I can be very focused and engaged in a conversation, until something triggers a thought about a task I need to take care of… I usually make sure not to forget it and only then can refocus on the conversation.</p><p><strong>Maggi Rubin Cohen, VP Product Management  </strong></p>		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_7.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_7.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_7-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>Although Emails and phone calls are a major distractor and part of my work; staying connected with our customers is a key and I usually stop everything and give them my professional answer and solution</p><p><strong>Eran Sandel, VP Sales</strong></p>  		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_1.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_1.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_1-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>Ubuntu... Ubuntu… Ubuntu…</p><p><strong>Philip Belder, CTO</strong></p>		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_8.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_8.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_8-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>Staying focused in my work is very important.<br />However, if I hear a song in the background that does not fit the atmosphere, I need to change it to ensure our customers and company receive the best support I can provide…</p><p><strong>Aviram Salomon, QA Manager</strong></p>		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_3.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_3.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_3-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>I’m mostly distracted by trying to juggle five things at a time.<br />Trying to accomplish too many tasks can certainly make me lose focus…</p><p><strong>Noga Mann, Customer Relations Representative</strong></p>		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_4.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_4.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_4-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>Disorganization can make me lose focus. When things are not organized the way I am used too I get easily distracted.</p><p><strong>Megi Franko, office and HR Manager</strong></p>		\n		<img width=\"250\" height=\"250\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_6.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_6.png 250w, https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/t_6-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px\" />		\n		<p>I often find myself being distracted by my cell phone even when it\'s completely silent…  Overtime, I have learned to hide it from sight, especially while working on attention- consuming projects.</p><p><strong>Keren Peleg, Product Manager</strong></p>', 'Our team', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '272-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-28 07:09:56', '2017-12-28 07:09:56', '', 272, 'https://axon.digitalim.co.il/2017/12/28/272-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
