(443, 1, '2017-12-28 13:04:17', '2017-12-28 13:04:17', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The Attention Test that is at the heart of the system is brought to you by Neurotech Solutions, a world leader in the field of attention, and as such, substantial clinical and developmental efforts have been invested in the test in order to maximize its accuracy and usefulness.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Our attention test is a standardized, comparative, Continuous Performance Test. The test is on-line, and requires only an internet connected PC and a set of headphones. </p>		\n			<h2>You can run two versions:</h2>		\n		<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>The system will choose the test </strong><strong>automatically</strong><strong> based on the child’s date </strong><strong>Of birth</strong></p>		\n			<figure><img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/icon_1.png\" alt=\"icon_1\" title=\"icon_1\"></figure><h3>ONE FOR CHILDREN (6-12)</h3><p>14 minutes</p>		\n			<figure><img src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/icon_2.png\" alt=\"icon_2\" title=\"icon_2\"></figure><h3>ONE FOR TEENS  (13-18)</h3><p>18 minutes</p>		\n		<p>The child needs to react by pressing the spacebar to a target element.In the children version</p>		\n		<p>they should react to a target of a figure we call HYPER</p>		\n		<img width=\"213\" height=\"194\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/target-children.jpg\" alt=\"\" />		\n		<p>or to a card of 3 </p>		\n		<p>hearts for the teens version</p>		\n		<img width=\"208\" height=\"275\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/target-adults.png\" alt=\"\" />		\n		<p>ny other element that appears at the center should be </p>		\n		<p>ignored</p>		\n		<img width=\"314\" height=\"409\" src=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/non-target-giraff.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://axon.digitalim.co.il/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/non-target-giraff.jpg